Package: EWMApchart
Type: Package
Title: EWMA-p chart
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Cheng-Kuan Lin, Li-Pang Chen, Su-Fen Yang 
Maintainer: Cheng-Kuan Lin <zore2023852@gmail.com>
Description: This package can simulate the discrete data with measurement error, convert continuous data to discrete data by sign statistic, compute the control limit of EWMA-p chart and adjusted EWMA-p chart for two one-sided chart or two-sided chart, and plot the EWMA-p chart and adjusted EWMA-p chart for input data.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports: qcr, stats, graphics
LazyData: true
